Interface Driver

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AbstractFactoryDriver, CommonDriver, EquinoxDriver, ExternalDriver
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractFactoryDriverImpl, CommonDriverImpl, DriverImpl, EquinoxDriverImpl, ExternalDriverImpl

    public interface Driver
    A representation of the model object 'Driver'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Name
    • Node
